data.description: This five bedroom 2721 sq ft home offers so much space and located in a gated community and in a culdesac with a greenbelt view in the front. Features two living areas, fireplace, separate dining room, and open kitchen with upgraded granite countertops. All laminate floors and no carpet and freshly painted interior. Very spacious private backyard offers great shade with covered patio and brand new privacy fence.
